name: ncpdp_prov_id
description: NCPDP Number of the provider

name: legal_business_nm
description: Legal Business Name

name: dba_nm
description: The DBA (Doing Business As) name of the provider

name: doctor_nm
description: Doctor's Name - Only set if the Primary Provider Type = 7 (Non-Pharmacy Dispensing Site), and the Provider Class = 7 (Alternate Dispensing Site)

name: store_num
description: The store number (usually assigned by parent company) associated with the provider.

name: phys_loc_addr_1
description: The physical location of the store and first line of the address.

name: phys_loc_addr_2
description: The physical location and second address line.

name: phys_loc_city
description: Physical location city of provider.

name: phys_loc_state_cd
description: The two-digit state code.

name: phys_loc_zip
description: This field identifies the 5 or 9 digit zip code of the provider, less dash marks.

name: phys_loc_phone_num
description: The physical site phone number.

name: phys_loc_phone_ext
description: The physical site phone extension.

name: phys_loc_phone_fax
description: The physical site FAX number.

name: phys_loc_email
description: E-mail address of pharmacy.

name: phys_loc_dir_txt
description: Text stating cross street or directions for physical location of provider.

name: phys_loc_cnty_cd
description: 5-digit FIPS code. The County FIPS code field and the County Name field identify the “most prevalent” county for the 5-digit ZIP code listed in a given record.

name: phys_loc_msa_cd
description: 4-digit MSA field contains the Metropolitan Statistical Area code, if any, in which some or all of the ZIP code lies.

name: phys_loc_pmsa_cd
description: 4-digit PMSA field contains the Primary Metropolitan Statistical Area code, if any, in which some or all of the ZIP code lies.

name: phys_loc_24_hr_flg
description: This field indicates whether this provider operates 24 hours a day. "Y" = Yes, "N" = No

name: phys_loc_prov_hrs_cd
description: Operating hours in seven segments (DOOCC). D = Day of the Week (Sunday = 1, Saturday = 7), OO = 2 digit Open Code, CC = 2 digit Close Code

name: phys_loc_vote_cd
description: Congressional voting district code.

name: phys_loc_lang_cd_1
description: Language Spoken Code (ISO 639-1 codes)

name: phys_loc_lang_cd_2
description: Language Spoken Code (ISO 639-1 codes)

name: phys_loc_lang_cd_3
description: Language Spoken Code (ISO 639-1 codes)

name: phys_loc_lang_cd_4
description: Language Spoken Code (ISO 639-1 codes)

name: phys_loc_lang_cd_5
description: Language Spoken Code (ISO 639-1 codes)

name: phys_loc_open_dt
description: Date of store opening. Zero if unknown

name: phys_loc_close_dt
description: Last business day of the site. Zeroes if not closed.

name: mail_addr_1
description: The first line of the mailing address.

name: mail_addr_2
description: The second line of the mailing address

name: mail_addr_city
description: Mailing Address City

name: mail_addr_state_cd
description: Mailing Address State code

name: mail_addr_zip_cd
description: This field identifies the 5 or 9 digit zip code of the mailing address, less dash marks.

name: contact_last_nm
description: Last name of primary contact person

name: contact_frst_nm
description: First name of primary contact person

name: contact_midl_nm
description: Middle initial of primary contact person

name: contact_title
description: Title of primary contact person

name: contact_phone_nm
description: Contact's phone number with area code

name: contact_phone_ext
description: Contact's phone extension

name: contact_email
description: Contact's email address

name: disp_cls_cd
description: The class code associated with this provider. The Dispenser Class Code is self-designated and is not related to taxonomy codes.

name: prmy_prov_typ_cd
description: This field contains the provider’s Provider type code. Blanks are not allowed.

name: secdy_prov_typ_cd
description: This field contains the provider’s Provider type code. blanks = none/not specified or not applicable in this field (provider does not specify a secondary type)

name: tertiary_prov_typ_cd
description: This field contains the provider’s dispenser type code. blanks = none/not specified or not applicable in this field (provider does not specify a tertiary type)

name: mdcr_prov_id
description: Medicare Provider (supplier) ID. The National Supplier Clearinghouse (NSC) is the organizational entity contracted by the Centers for Medicare & Medicaid Services (CMS) to issue Medicare billing privileges to suppliers of Durable Medical Equipment, Prosthetics, Orthotics and Supplies (DMEPOS) and to maintain a supplier file that contains information collected via the CMS 855S enrollment form.

name: npi
description: National Provider ID (NPI) - The standard unique health identifier for health care providers to use in filing and processing health care claims and other transactions. At the pharmacy or alternate dispensing site level.

name: dea_reg_id
description: DEA registration ID - This field contains the Drug Enforcement Administration (DEA) Number of the provider. Formerly called the Federal License Number on this file.

name: dea_exprtn_dt
description: The date the Drug Enforcement Administration (DEA) requires the federal license be renewed by.

name: tin
description: Federal Tax ID Number

name: state_tax_id_num
description: State Income Tax ID Number

name: deactivation_cd
description: Deactivation code - Code with reason for deactivation

name: reinstatement_cd
description: Reinstatement code - code with reason for reactivation of record

name: reinstatement_dt
description: Reinstatement date
